name: Dave Starbelly #27
description:
“MOAR” is an unusual mansion in the metaverse where 5,555 creatures with their souls minted with the ERC721 blockchain as NFTs. 
Guests staying at the MOAR, including humans, zombies and cyborgs, live peacefully together. Each is unique, hand-drawn by Spanish artist Joan Cornellà using over 180 unique attributes.
Here you can find shops, games, virtual exhibitions and…MOAR!
